# Documentation Standards

## Language

- **English** is the source for CLI, config tables, and generated guides.
- **Persian** and **Chinese** live under `docs/fa/` and `docs/zh/` (folder i18n) — see `.cursor/rules/i18n.mdc` and **`.cursor/rules/doc-locale-parity.mdc`**.
- Complete sentences; commands copy-paste ready (no `...` in code blocks).

## Repository map

| Path | Purpose | Edit manually? |
|------|---------|----------------|
| `docs/en/index.md` | Root hub (HTML) | Yes |
| `docs/en/cheatsheet/index.md` | Cheatsheet section home | Yes |
| `docs/en/arch/index.md` | Architecture section home | Yes |
| `docs/en/dev/index.md` | Develop section home | Yes |
| `docs/en/cheatsheet/cli/` | CLI by topic | Yes |
| `docs/en/cheatsheet/guides/` | Roles, scales, config deep dives | Mixed (see generators) |
| `docs/en/arch/rgw/` | RGW architecture & learning | Sync + manual |
| `docs/en/cheatsheet/config/` | Upstream option tables | **No** — `generate-config.py` |
| `reports/` | Generated content-inventory | **No** — `generate-content-inventory.py` |
| `REFERENCE.md` | Legacy reference table → `cheatsheet/OVERVIEW.md` | Yes, then `sync-docs-index.py` |

Layout reference: `scripts/LAYOUT.md` · path constants: `scripts/repo_paths.py`

## Linking

- Inside MkDocs: prefer directory URLs (`guides/quickstart/`) in hub HTML after `fix-html-hrefs.py`
- Config: `../config/<subsystem>/INDEX.md` or `./scripts/lookup-config.sh`
- Cross-link CLI ↔ config ↔ guides; do not duplicate large option tables in guides
- From `guides/`: readability guide at `../../readability-guide.md`

## CLI pages

- Group by task; one command per `bash` block
- `<placeholder>` for args; `[optional]` for flags
- “See also” → related config INDEX

## After prose edits

```bash
python3 scripts/setup-docs-layout.py
python3 scripts/sync-i18n-pages.py      # if HAND_PAGES source changed
python3 scripts/fix-html-hrefs.py       # if hub HTML edited
python3 scripts/validate-docs-paths.py
```

## Do not

- Hand-edit generated `config/` tables
- Add `Co-authored-by: Cursor` to commits
- Overwrite section hub `index.md` via `sync-docs-index.py`
